{"title":"[하모니카] NPM global 설치 해결법","date":"2019-11-21T13:10:00.000Z","link":"2019/11/21/13","tags":["ckir","hamonikr"],"categories":["ckir"],"updated":"2019-12-14T13:48:40.851Z","content":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/guides/blob/master/npm-global-without-sudo.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">정보 출처 : sindresorhus’ gist</a><br>\n<s>터미널은 vscode의 터미널을 이용하시면 편합니다</s></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-글로벌-패키지가-설치될-디렉토리를-생성합니다-create-a-directory-for-global-packages\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2019/11/21/13#1-글로벌-패키지가-설치될-디렉토리를-생성합니다-create-a-directory-for-global-packages\"></a>1. 글로벌 패키지가 설치될 디렉토리를 생성합니다 ~Create a directory for global packages~<a href=\"2019/11/21/13#1-글로벌-패키지가-설치될-디렉토리를-생성합니다-create-a-directory-for-global-packages\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-console\">mkdir &quot;${HOME}/.npm-packages&quot;  \n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"2-npm의-글로벌-패키지-설치-위치를-설정합니다-tell-npm-where-to-store-globally-installed-packages\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2019/11/21/13#2-npm의-글로벌-패키지-설치-위치를-설정합니다-tell-npm-where-to-store-globally-installed-packages\"></a>2. npm의 글로벌 패키지 설치 위치를 설정합니다  ~Tell npm where to store globally installed packages~<a href=\"2019/11/21/13#2-npm의-글로벌-패키지-설치-위치를-설정합니다-tell-npm-where-to-store-globally-installed-packages\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-console\">npm config set prefix &quot;${HOME}/.npm-packages&quot;  \n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"2-npm의-글로벌-패키지-설치-위치를-설정합니다-tell-npm-where-to-store-globally-installed-packages-v2\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2019/11/21/13#2-npm의-글로벌-패키지-설치-위치를-설정합니다-tell-npm-where-to-store-globally-installed-packages-v2\"></a>2. npm의 글로벌 패키지 설치 위치를 설정합니다  ~Tell npm where to store globally installed packages~<a href=\"2019/11/21/13#2-npm의-글로벌-패키지-설치-위치를-설정합니다-tell-npm-where-to-store-globally-installed-packages-v2\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-console\">npm config set prefix &quot;${HOME}/.npm-packages&quot;  \n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"3-npm이-설치된-바이너리-및-매뉴얼-페이지를-찾도록-설정합니다-ensure-npm-will-find-installed-binaries-and-man-pages\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2019/11/21/13#3-npm이-설치된-바이너리-및-매뉴얼-페이지를-찾도록-설정합니다-ensure-npm-will-find-installed-binaries-and-man-pages\"></a>3. npm이 설치된 바이너리 및 매뉴얼 페이지를 찾도록 설정합니다  ~Ensure npm will find installed binaries and man pages~<a href=\"2019/11/21/13#3-npm이-설치된-바이너리-및-매뉴얼-페이지를-찾도록-설정합니다-ensure-npm-will-find-installed-binaries-and-man-pages\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-console\">NPM_PACKAGES=&quot;${HOME}/.npm-packages&quot;  \nexport PATH=&quot;$PATH:$NPM_PACKAGES/bin&quot;  \nexport MANPATH=&quot;${MANPATH-$(manpath)}:$NPM_PACKAGES/share/man&quot;  \n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"4-bashrc-파일을-다시-로드합니다\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2019/11/21/13#4-bashrc-파일을-다시-로드합니다\"></a>4. .bashrc 파일을 다시 로드합니다<a href=\"2019/11/21/13#4-bashrc-파일을-다시-로드합니다\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-console\">source ~/.bashrc\n</code></pre>\n","next":{"title":"[하모니카] ESukmeans님의 사지방 유튜브 접속기","link":"2019/11/21/12"},"plink":"https://present.kim/2019/11/21/13/"}